<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title>MINCHO</title>
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/loginRegister.css' />
    <!-- 파비콘 -->
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <link rel="icon" href="/images/favicon.ico" type="image/x-icon">
    <!-- 제이쿼리 -->
    <script  src="http://code.jquery.com/jquery-latest.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://kit.fontawesome.com/64d58efce2.js" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
  </head>
  <body class="login-body">
    <%- include('title') %>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="forms-container">
            <div class="signin-signup">
                <form action="/login" class="sign-in-form" method="POST">
                    <h2 class="title">Sign in</h2>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Userid" name="id" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="pw" required>
                    </div>
                    <input type="submit" value="Login" class="btn solid">

                    <p class="social-text">Or Sign in with social platforms</p>
                    <div class="social-media">
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </form>

                <form action="/register" class="sign-up-form" method="POST">
                    <h2 class="title">Sign up</h2>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Userid" name="id" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="text" placeholder="Username" name="name" required>
                    </div>
                    <div class="input-field">
                        <i class="fas fa-user"></i>
                        <input type="password" placeholder="Password" name="pw" required>
                    </div>
                    <input type="submit" value="Sign up" class="btn solid">

                    <p class="social-text">Or Sign up with social platforms</p>
                    <div class="social-media">
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-facebook-f"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-twitter"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-google"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
                            <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </form>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="panels-container">
            <div class="panel left-panel">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>회원이 아니신가요?</h3>
                    <p>
                        MINCHO 거래소에 처음 오셨나요? 어서 가입하고 축하금 1000원을 받으세요! 저렴한 수수료로 거래하고 수익을 챙겨가세요!
                    </p>
                    <button class="btn transparent" id="sign-up-btn">Sign up</button>
                </div>
                <img src="/images/metrics.svg" class="image" alt="">
            </div>

            <div class="panel right-panel">
                <div class="content">
                    <h3>가입하셨나요?</h3>
                    <p>
                        회원이시면 국내 1등 거래소 MINCHO에 거래를 시작하세요! 국내 최저 거래 수수료 0.05%로 수익을 가져가세요!
                    </p>
                    <button class="btn transparent" id="sign-in-btn">Sign in</button>
                </div>
                <img src="/images/social.svg" class="image" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="/javascripts/login.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
